name: Apache Sunrise - Lenticular Clouds
description:
Apache Sunrise is a song  included in the album “Joy of Humans” published in 2012 by Egyptian Maraccas. The music and the visuals were presented live at Oi! Rio de Janeiro festival Novas Frequências 2012 where Lenticular Clouds took part.
This is the first limited 100 copies edition of the song and the .gif that appeared in the album launch website.
